title: Fox Surf Presents | Caroline Marks, The Future Is Now
description:
This summer Fox Surf’s Caroline Marks earned herself a spot in the history books. Winning every competitive title you can as a women’s amateur surfer in the United States, Caroline won the U.S. Championships, the Volcom World Championships and multiple NSSA National titles. We recently spent some time with her in Southern California and got a little insight into her feelings towards winning, coaching, ear plugs and Hawaiian-style poki. 

Music:
The Morning Stars’
"Murder of Roman Polanski"

Edit:
Jensen Young Sik
